                <br />
                <b>Repeat notifications sent automatically</b>
                <p style="font-size:12px">
                    As repeat notifications come up the Repeat system can automatically send them out to the subscribers without requiring any manual intervention from you.
                    <br />
                    <br />
                    Alternatively, this setting can be disabled allowing you to manually send out each repeat notification for the day. The daily email will remind you
                    of which repeats are due for the day, at which point you can login to the Repeat website and manually send them out one by one.
