                <p style="font-size:12px">
                    Reports can be viewed and downloaded to see how many upcoming repeat entries are due for this week, month, year etc. This will allow you to forecast
                    the number of sales you can expect going forward i.e. how many customers will have upcoming repeats in the near future.
                    <br />
                    <br />
